<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Beyazit Cargo - App Jastip Single HTML</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f5f7fb;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --ink: #102033;
      --muted: #68778a;
      --line: #dbe3ef;
      --primary: #123e68;
      --primary-2: #0b7c86;
      --accent: #f2b84b;
      --danger: #d64545;
      --success: #0c8f5b;
      --warning: #c98412;
      --shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(16, 32, 51, 0.10);
      --radius: 22px;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(11, 124, 134, .12), transparent 32rem),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(242, 184, 75, .14), transparent 28rem),
        var(--bg);
      color: var(--ink);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    button, input, textarea, select { font: inherit; }
    button { cursor: pointer; border: 0; }
    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
    .app-shell { min-height: 100vh; }
    .topbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      background: rgba(245, 247, 251, .78);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(219, 227, 239, .8);
    }
    .topbar-inner {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      min-width: 220px;
    }
    .brand-mark {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-2));
      color: white;
      font-weight: 900;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 22px rgba(18, 62, 104, .24);
    }
    .brand-title { font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -.04em; font-size: 18px; }
    .brand-subtitle { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: -2px; }
    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .nav button {
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 750;
    }
    .nav button.active {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(18, 62, 104, .18);
    }
    .top-actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      gap: 10px;
      min-width: 220px;
    }
    .pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 10px 13px;
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 800;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(16, 32, 51, .05);
    }
    .pill.primary { background: var(--primary); color: white; border-color: var(--primary); }
    .pill.accent { background: var(--accent); color: #2d210b; border-color: var(--accent); }
    .pill.danger { background: #fff1f1; color: var(--danger); border-color: #ffd1d1; }
    .container {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 24px 18px 80px;
    }
    .hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.25fr .75fr;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: stretch;
      margin-top: 14px;
    }
    .hero-card {
      border-radius: 34px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(18, 62, 104, .96), rgba(11, 124, 134, .92)),
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(242, 184, 75, .45), transparent 22rem);
      color: white;
      padding: 36px;
      min-height: 360px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-card::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      width: 360px;
      height: 360px;
      right: -100px;
      bottom: -120px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .12);
    }
    .hero-kicker {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .14);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .22);
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(34px, 6vw, 64px);
      line-height: .96;
      letter-spacing: -.07em;
      margin: 22px 0 14px;
      max-width: 720px;
    }
    .hero p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .82);
      max-width: 680px;
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .hero-buttons { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; margin-top: 24px; }
    .hero-btn {
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      font-weight: 900;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .hero-btn.light { background: white; color: var(--primary); }
    .hero-btn.dark { background: rgba(255,255,255,.12); color: white; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.25); }
    .hero-side {
      border-radius: 34px;
      background: var(--card);
      padding: 22px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      border: 1px solid rgba(219, 227, 239, .8);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .mini-card {
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: #fff;
      padding: 18px;
    }
    .mini-title { font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -.03em; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .mini-text { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.55; font-size: 14px; }
    .stats-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .stat {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(16, 32, 51, .05);
    }
    .stat-value { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 950; letter-spacing: -.05em; }
    .stat-label { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 4px; }
    .section {
      display: none;
      animation: fadeIn .18s ease;
    }
    .section.active { display: block; }
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: end;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      margin: 28px 0 18px;
    }
    .section-head h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);
      letter-spacing: -.06em;
    }
    .section-head p {
      margin: 8px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 650px;
    }
    .toolbar {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 190px 170px;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .input, .select, .textarea {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: white;
      border-radius: 17px;
      padding: 13px 14px;
      color: var(--ink);
      outline: none;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(16, 32, 51, .035);
    }
    .textarea { min-height: 120px; resize: vertical; line-height: 1.6; }
    .input:focus, .select:focus, .textarea:focus {
      border-color: rgba(11, 124, 134, .55);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(11, 124, 134, .09);
    }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .product-card {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(16, 32, 51, .06);
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: 100%;
    }
    .product-img {
      height: 190px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ecf4ff, #fff7e6);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-size: 62px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .product-badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: 13px;
      left: 13px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.9);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 7px 10px;
      font-weight: 850;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    .product-body { padding: 17px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; flex: 1; }
    .product-title { font-weight: 950; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -.035em; }
    .product-desc { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.55; min-height: 40px; }
    .product-meta {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: auto;
    }
    .tag {
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 7px 10px;
      background: #f1f5f9;
      color: #475569;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }
    .price-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: end;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }
    .price { font-weight: 950; font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: -.04em; }
    .fee { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }
    .btn {
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      font-weight: 900;
      background: #eef5ff;
      color: var(--primary);
      display: inline-flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      transition: transform .15s ease, box-shadow .15s ease, opacity .15s ease;
    }
    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(16, 32, 51, .09); }
    .btn.primary { background: var(--primary); color: white; }
    .btn.secondary { background: var(--primary-2); color: white; }
    .btn.accent { background: var(--accent); color: #2d210b; }
    .btn.danger { background: #fff1f1; color: var(--danger); }
    .btn.ghost { background: white; border: 1px solid var(--line); color: var(--ink); }
    .btn.block { width: 100%; }
    .btn.small { padding: 8px 10px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 12px; }
    .cart-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 360px;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .panel {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(16, 32, 51, .06);
      padding: 18px;
    }
    .panel h3 {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      font-size: 22px;
      letter-spacing: -.045em;
    }
    .cart-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 54px 1fr auto;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 14px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      align-items: center;
    }
    .cart-item:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
    .cart-icon {
      width: 54px;
      height: 54px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: #f1f5f9;
      font-size: 25px;
    }
    .cart-name { font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -.02em; }
    .cart-note { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; margin-top: 3px; }
    .qty {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      justify-content: end;
    }
    .qty button {
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #eef5ff;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    .qty span {
      min-width: 24px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 900;
    }
    .summary-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 10px 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--line);
    }
    .summary-row strong { color: var(--ink); }
    .summary-row.total {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: var(--ink);
      border-bottom: 0;
      padding-top: 14px;
    }
    .form-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .form-grid .wide { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
    .label {
      display: block;
      font-weight: 850;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 7px;
    }
    .empty-state {
      border: 1px dashed #b8c5d6;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 34px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.55);
    }
    .empty-state .emoji { font-size: 44px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .toast {
      position: fixed;
      right: 18px;
      bottom: 18px;
      background: #102033;
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(16,32,51,.24);
      transform: translateY(120px);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: .2s ease;
      z-index: 100;
      max-width: 340px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }
    .toast.show { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
    .order-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 16px;
      background: white;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .order-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: start;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .order-id { font-weight: 950; letter-spacing: -.035em; }
    .order-date { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; margin-top: 3px; }
    .status {
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 7px 10px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 900;
      background: #eef5ff;
      color: var(--primary);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .status.pending { background: #fff7e6; color: #9a6700; }
    .status.process { background: #e7fbff; color: #08717a; }
    .status.done { background: #e9fff4; color: #0c7f52; }
    .status.cancel { background: #fff1f1; color: #b93333; }
    .admin-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 380px 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .table-wrap {
      overflow: auto;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 20px;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      min-width: 680px;
      background: white;
    }
    th, td {
      text-align: left;
      padding: 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-size: 13px;
      vertical-align: top;
    }
    th {
      background: #f8fafc;
      color: #475569;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .05em;
    }
    tr:last-child td { border-bottom: 0; }
    .invoice-box {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      max-width: 820px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    .invoice-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink);
      padding-bottom: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .invoice-brand { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 950; letter-spacing: -.055em; }
    .invoice-muted { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; font-size: 13px; }
    .invoice-total {
      text-align: right;
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: -.055em;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .note-box {
      border-radius: 22px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: #f8fafc;
      padding: 16px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .two-col {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .timeline {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .timeline-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 42px 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .timeline-num {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      font-weight: 950;
    }
    .timeline-card {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 14px;
    }
    .timeline-card b { display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .timeline-card span { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.55; font-size: 14px; }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 34px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .hidden { display: none !important; }
    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .cart-layout, .admin-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .toolbar { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .topbar-inner { align-items: flex-start; flex-direction: column; }
      .brand, .top-actions { min-width: 0; width: 100%; }
      .top-actions { justify-content: flex-start; }
      .nav { justify-content: flex-start; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .container { padding: 18px 12px 80px; }
      .hero-card { padding: 24px; border-radius: 26px; }
      .hero-side, .panel, .invoice-box { border-radius: 24px; }
      .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .form-grid, .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .section-head { display: block; }
      .cart-item { grid-template-columns: 46px 1fr; }
      .qty { grid-column: 1 / -1; justify-content: flex-start; }
      .invoice-head { display: block; }
      .invoice-total { text-align: left; }
    }
    @media print {
      body { background: white; }
      .topbar, .footer, .no-print { display: none !important; }
      .container { padding: 0; max-width: none; }
      .section { display: block !important; }
      .section:not(#invoiceSection) { display: none !important; }
      .invoice-box { border: 0; box-shadow: none; border-radius: 0; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="app-shell">
    <header class="topbar no-print">
      <div class="topbar-inner">
        <div class="brand">
          <div class="brand-mark">BC</div>
          <div>
            <div class="brand-title">Beyazit Cargo</div>
            <div class="brand-subtitle">App jastip single HTML</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <nav class="nav" id="navTabs">
          <button class="active" data-section="homeSection">Home</button>
          <button data-section="catalogSection">Katalog</button>
          <button data-section="cartSection">Keranjang</button>
          <button data-section="ordersSection">Order</button>
          <button data-section="adminSection">Admin</button>
          <button data-section="invoiceSection">Invoice</button>
        </nav>
        <div class="top-actions">
          <button class="pill" id="quickSearchBtn">🔎 Cari</button>
          <button class="pill primary" id="cartNavBtn">🛒 <span id="cartCount">0</span></button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main class="container">
      <section class="section active" id="homeSection">
        <div class="hero">
          <div class="hero-card">
            <div class="hero-kicker">⚡ Cepat · Aman · Terpercaya</div>
            <h1>Jastip modern dalam satu file HTML.</h1>
            <p>Kelola katalog produk, hitung fee jastip otomatis, masukkan produk ke keranjang, buat pesanan, dan cetak invoice langsung dari browser tanpa database.</p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
              <button class="hero-btn light" onclick="showSection('catalogSection')">Mulai Belanja</button>
              <button class="hero-btn dark" onclick="showSection('adminSection')">Kelola Produk</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-side">
            <div class="mini-card">
              <div class="mini-title">Untuk jualan jastip</div>
              <div class="mini-text">Cocok untuk open PO, jastip barang luar kota, jastip bandara, jastip skincare, fashion, makanan, dan merchandise.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="mini-card">
              <div class="mini-title">Tanpa server</div>
              <div class="mini-text">Data tersimpan di LocalStorage browser. Bisa diedit, reset, export, dan import.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="mini-card">
              <div class="mini-title">Invoice siap print</div>
              <div class="mini-text">Setelah checkout, invoice bisa langsung dicetak atau disalin untuk dikirim ke pelanggan.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stats-grid">
          <div class="stat"><div class="stat-value" id="statProducts">0</div><div class="stat-label">Produk aktif</div></div>
          <div class="stat"><div class="stat-value" id="statOrders">0</div><div class="stat-label">Order tersimpan</div></div>
          <div class="stat"><div class="stat-value" id="statRevenue">Rp0</div><div class="stat-label">Total transaksi</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <h2>Cara kerja app</h2>
            <p>Alur sederhana untuk customer dan admin jastip.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-num">1</div>
            <div class="timeline-card">
              <b>Pilih produk</b>
              <span>Customer memilih barang dari katalog yang sudah kamu siapkan.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-num">2</div>
            <div class="timeline-card">
              <b>Masuk keranjang</b>
              <span>Harga barang, fee, dan estimasi ongkir dihitung otomatis.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
